    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1837730/extras/d8f3bb311750faef1c5011310f56198b.poster.avif?t=1771886992\" width=1170 height=618 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1837730/extras/d8f3bb311750faef1c5011310f56198b.webm?t=1771886992\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1837730/extras/d8f3bb311750faef1c5011310f56198b.mp4?t=1771886992\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>清单</strong> ▶ 窃取清单上的一切！清单上可能有任何东西——见机行事。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1837730/extras/312626d1e1671ba4461cc93a8fd744d6.poster.avif?t=1771886992\" width=1170 height=618 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1837730/extras/312626d1e1671ba4461cc93a8fd744d6.webm?t=1771886992\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1837730/extras/312626d1e1671ba4461cc93a8fd744d6.mp4?t=1771886992\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>世界</strong> ▶ 搬空银行金库、潜入政府大楼、寻找黑帮藏匿点，不要忘记其他地区。每个地方都是发财的机会。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1837730/extras/020823f448dd2eb2f19fc41208516dad.poster.avif?t=1771886992\" width=1170 height=618 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1837730/extras/020823f448dd2eb2f19fc41208516dad.webm?t=1771886992\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1837730/extras/020823f448dd2eb2f19fc41208516dad.mp4?t=1771886992\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>物理</strong> ▶ 把物品堆积起来爬到难以进入的区域，或者直接随处扔物品。干嘛不乱扔呢？ <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1837730/extras/d89fae6a773172bb2efed5e6f4f54d34.poster.avif?t=1771886992\" width=1170 height=618 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1837730/extras/d89fae6a773172bb2efed5e6f4f54d34.webm?t=1771886992\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1837730/extras/d89fae6a773172bb2efed5e6f4f54d34.mp4?t=1771886992\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>互动</strong> ▶ 你是想窃取访问密码并小心翼翼地解除安保系统，还是在工作中带个炸弹给警察一点颜色看看？由你做主。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1837730/extras/388bc2d813036df20664766c4f2657ee.poster.avif?t=1771886992\" width=1170 height=618 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1837730/extras/388bc2d813036df20664766c4f2657ee.webm?t=1771886992\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1837730/extras/388bc2d813036df20664766c4f2657ee.mp4?t=1771886992\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>升级</strong> ▶ 成为一名大盗——解锁最困难的劫盗任务，使用不可思议的装备来完成。还有，别忘了买房子!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1837730/extras/57799eb1168f3daf8dc20a4033f371ee.poster.avif?t=1771886992\" width=1170 height=618 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1837730/extras/57799eb1168f3daf8dc20a4033f371ee.webm?t=1771886992\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1837730/extras/57799eb1168f3daf8dc20a4033f371ee.mp4?t=1771886992\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>合作 （2-4人）</strong>▶ 人多更好玩！和你的伙伴们一起行窃，或者正好相反——成为警察，阻止他们偷东西。</p>",
